</h3><p>A tweak tool to customize the GNOME Shell and to disable UI elements.</p>
<p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@justperfection:gnome.org">Just Perfection</a> reports</p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/3843/just-perfection/">Just Perfection extension</a> version 20 has been released with some bug fixes and two new features (calendar and events visibility).
This version is named after Francesco Hayez (Italian painter).

<img src="https://thisweek.gnome.org/posts/2022/04/twig-37/bdb32a0e4df4a1d783df171f049ecaaaecb9bb66.png" alt="" />
